    'dimming':   '<strong>1-10V analog dimming ships standard on every Anaheim SKU</strong> \u2014 no upgrade tier, no separate dimming variant, no extra BOM line. Wire the violet/grey 1-10V leads from the driver to your scheduling system, dimmer, or DALI gateway and Anaheim dims smoothly from <strong>100% down to ~10%</strong> output. Pair with a quick' + "\u24B6" + 'DAPT controller for occupancy + photocell + scheduling on the same gateway, or wire direct to a building management system. The driver is heat-isolated from the LED module \u2014 no thermal foldback at low-dim states, no flicker on the rebound. For sites without a central control system, see the <code>/PA</code> photocell tab.',
